 Menu: @{fg shine}Paint@{fg text}
 Item: @{fg shine}Bevel Box Type@{fg text}

 Subs: @{fg shine}Single@{fg text}
       @{fg shine}Button@{fg text}
       @{fg shine}Ridge@{fg text}
       @{fg shine}Dropbox@{fg text}

 Changes the frame style of the draw bevel box tool.


 Sub: @{fg shine}Recessed@{fg text}

 The bevel box will appear recessed.


 Sub: @{fg shine}Filled@{fg text}

 Fills the bevel box with the current draw pen color.
