       @{fg shine}13%@{fg text}
       @{fg shine}7%@{fg text}
       @{fg shine}Bars@{fg text}
       @{fg shine}Lines@{fg text}

 Changes the dithering appearance.


 @{i}@{u}Notes@{ui}@{uu}

 There is are keyboard and gadget equivalents.


 Sub: @{fg shine}Transparent?@{fg text}

 Only one color will be used, and the background will show through.
@endnode

