 Sub: @{fg shine}Load Palette...@{fg text}

 Loads a palette into either the global colormap, or if possible, into the individual colormap.


 Sub: @{fg shine}Save Palette...@{fg text}

 Saves the current palette to disk.


 Subs: @{fg shine}MagicWB Preset@{fg text}
       @{fg shine}NewIcon Preset@{fg text}
       @{fg shine}RomIcon Preset@{fg text}
       @{fg shine}JBCIcon Preset@{fg text}
       @{fg shine}Iconographix Preset@{fg text}

