 Menu: @{fg shine}Paint@{fg text}
 Item: @{fg shine}Load Preferences@{fg text}

 Resets Iconian to use a specified preference file.


 @{i}@{u}Notes@{ui}@{uu}

 Iconian saves preferences in IFF chunks.  A preference file may contain only one setting, or many.
@endnode

